<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Thuật Toán - Bộ sưu tập - Kaizen - tốt hơn mỗi ngày</title><link>https://vanvuvuong.github.io/collections/thu%E1%BA%ADt-to%C3%A1n/</link><description>Kaizen - tốt hơn mỗi ngày</description><generator>Hugo 0.152.0 &amp; FixIt v0.4.0-alpha.2</generator><language>vi</language><managingEditor>kaizen-vn-team@proton.me (Kaizen Teams)</managingEditor><webMaster>kaizen-vn-team@proton.me (Kaizen Teams)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Mon, 12 Jan 2026 11:04:48 +0700</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://vanvuvuong.github.io/collections/thu%E1%BA%ADt-to%C3%A1n/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>5. Đồ Thị Có Trọng Số (Weighted Graphs)</title><link>https://vanvuvuong.github.io/bai-viet/khoa-hoc-may-tinh/algorithm-manual/theory-explain/weighted-graphs/</link><pubDate>Mon, 12 Jan 2026 10:17:32 +0700</pubDate><author>kaizen-vn-team@proton.me (Kaizen Teams)</author><guid>https://vanvuvuong.github.io/bai-viet/khoa-hoc-may-tinh/algorithm-manual/theory-explain/weighted-graphs/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="heading-element" id="khác-gì-với-chapter-7"&gt;&lt;span&gt;KHÁC GÌ VỚI CHAPTER 7?&lt;/span&gt;
